data.description: Absolutely adorable cozy cottage within walking distance to the beach!  This home is very warm and inviting with it's screened in front porch and nice open back porch which leads to large, fenced in back yard.  Plenty of room for grilling and entertaining. Could be perfect for anyone looking for a first home, to downsize or a really great investment property!  Literally one block from the beach.  Great scenery and neighborhood all around.  Call today to see this little beauty!
